01:05:24.720 --> 01:05:34.640
As we have seen, we must hear Him.

01:05:34.640 --> 01:05:41.359
We must hear him.

01:05:41.359 --> 01:05:56.240
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we always hear you.

01:05:56.240 --> 01:06:01.200
And I thank you, Lord.

01:06:01.200 --> 01:06:13.648
We pray for the families that are grieving tonight.

01:06:13.648 --> 01:06:56.630
We pray for the families that are hurting tonight.

01:07:17.232 --> 01:07:17.680
And I thank you, Lord, that they find you in the midst of the storm.

01:07:51.520 --> 01:07:54.275
They run to you in the midst of the storm.

01:07:54.275 --> 01:08:33.220
Many probably are upset at you and blaming you and saying, "Oh, curse the Lord," and all the things they want to say because they're hurting and they're grieving.

01:08:33.220 --> 01:09:08.760
But Father, in the midst of the darkest hour, Father, I thank you, Lord, that you become lighter and lighter to them and their heart is filled with peace and joy, knowing that they're on the other side waiting on them if they know you.

01:09:08.760 --> 01:09:14.619
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we find you, we know you, we hear you, and we abide in you.

01:09:15.569 --> 01:09:28.827
And you said, "If ye abide in me, if my words remain in you, ask what you will, and it shall be done.

01:10:20.800 --> 01:10:21.190
" And we thank you, Lord, for the blood tonight, Father, that covers us, every single one of us, in these dark days ahead, the blood covers us in Jesus' name.

01:10:21.190 --> 01:10:23.140
Thank you, Lord.

01:10:23.140 --> 01:11:12.800
Now, I do that all the time, praying over my family, praying over our finances.

01:11:12.800 --> 01:11:17.128
And that's just what we do.

01:11:24.000 --> 01:11:27.547
I think it's important that you do that.

01:11:48.708 --> 01:11:48.960
Now, people say, "I don't agree.

01:11:48.960 --> 01:11:51.120
" That's fine, don't do it.

01:12:13.556 --> 01:12:13.751
But I'm going to, you know, and there's fruit.

01:12:13.751 --> 01:12:14.729
I believe there's fruit.

01:12:14.729 --> 01:12:18.453
He protects those that he loves.

01:12:18.453 --> 01:12:19.813
I believe it.

01:12:43.120 --> 01:12:43.646
He's going to protect you.

01:12:43.646 --> 01:12:50.995
Believe it today when we see disaster happen.

01:12:56.533 --> 01:12:57.333
And you say, "Why are the little girls going...?

01:12:57.333 --> 01:13:05.493
" Always stay on God's side.

01:13:05.493 --> 01:13:08.560
I don't know why.

01:13:16.213 --> 01:13:26.272
I know the Bible says the enemy comes, and he's a thief, and he comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

01:13:26.272 --> 01:13:35.352
That's what I know.

01:13:49.661 --> 01:13:49.893
God comes that we might have life, and life more abundantly.

01:13:49.893 --> 01:13:50.355
Yes.

01:14:15.520 --> 01:14:28.537
So regardless if I understand, regardless of what happens, I always stay on God's side, and I go, "God, thank you.

01:14:28.537 --> 01:14:29.189
You're so good.

01:14:29.189 --> 01:14:35.260
" Regardless if I understand why all this happened, why these people...

01:14:35.260 --> 01:14:39.109
People always say, "Why did God do that?

01:14:39.109 --> 01:14:41.080
" God didn't do it.

01:14:41.080 --> 01:14:43.480
God doesn't kill.

01:14:43.480 --> 01:14:45.600
God doesn't steal, and he doesn't destroy.

01:14:45.600 --> 01:14:54.410
God is a good God and the devil's a bad devil.

01:14:54.410 --> 01:14:56.719
It's the devil that does this.

01:14:56.719 --> 01:15:01.537
Now, it's our choice if we apply the blood and we open the door.

01:15:01.537 --> 01:15:08.251
Now, if we open the door to sin, ladies and gentlemen, you open the door and you've got open doors.

01:15:09.813 --> 01:15:12.959
The devil comes in like a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

01:15:12.959 --> 01:15:15.640
Who is he not able to devour?

01:15:16.939 --> 01:15:18.880
The ones that are underneath the blood and understand their covenant.

01:15:18.880 --> 01:15:26.159
I believe that he gives power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you.

01:15:26.159 --> 01:15:36.229
You have to believe it, though, and you have to have that inside your heart.

01:15:36.239 --> 01:15:44.680
It doesn't come by only saying it one time and quoting Psalms 91 one time.

01:15:58.840 --> 01:15:59.309
It says faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

01:16:03.919 --> 01:16:16.711
And the only way you're going to get ahead in these last days is having a change from the inside out, getting this word of God foundation and this priority, putting it in your eyes and renewing your mind and going from glory to glory.

01:16:16.711 --> 01:16:26.700
Psalms 91 is what you have to live by and say, and even if you see something bad happen, I stay on God's side just like Job.

01:16:26.700 --> 01:16:28.720
Father, I thank you.

01:16:28.720 --> 01:16:32.549
"Though you slay me," like he said, "yet will I praise you.

01:16:32.549 --> 01:16:34.304
" And it wasn't him.

01:16:34.304 --> 01:16:37.386
I'm just saying Job opened the door.

01:16:37.386 --> 01:16:39.280
God is a good God.

01:16:39.280 --> 01:16:41.257
The devil is a bad devil.

01:16:45.546 --> 01:16:49.400
It's like Oral Roberts used to say, "Don't walk in fear, and don't do things out of fear.

01:16:49.400 --> 01:16:52.440
Fear tolerated is faith contaminated.

01:16:52.440 --> 01:16:58.880
" You've got to walk in faith and say, "Father, regardless, I thank you, Lord, today.

01:16:58.880 --> 01:16:59.600
You're good.

01:17:02.260 --> 01:17:08.800
I believe you're a rewarder of those that diligently seek you.

01:17:09.600 --> 01:17:11.956
You have a plan for my life.

01:17:12.667 --> 01:17:27.280
I know, Father, regardless of the signs of the times and the circumstances, even if I miss it, what the devil meant for bad, God, you're going to turn it around for good in my favor today.

01:17:27.280 --> 01:17:31.950
But I'm always going to stay on the right side and know that God is a good God.

01:17:31.950 --> 01:17:34.140
" So that's what you have to stay.

01:17:34.140 --> 01:17:38.010
Even whenever you see bad things happen to good people, God's a good God.

01:17:39.304 --> 01:17:41.712
I refuse to sit there and let my mind go there.

01:17:44.128 --> 01:17:45.246
You go, "Oh, why did that happen to so many little girls?

01:17:47.590 --> 01:17:47.800
" I refuse to let my mind go there.

01:17:47.800 --> 01:17:48.960
God's a good God.

01:17:49.280 --> 01:17:50.880
The devil's a bad devil.

01:17:55.280 --> 01:17:56.200
And the devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

01:17:56.200 --> 01:18:01.333
God came that we might have life, and life more abundantly.

01:18:01.333 --> 01:18:02.300
Open doors happen.

01:18:02.300 --> 01:18:02.870
Things happen.

01:18:02.870 --> 01:18:04.222
We live in a fallen world.

01:18:04.222 --> 01:18:11.760
But I refuse to say things that get in my mouth.

01:18:17.466 --> 01:18:17.840
People say in their heart all the time, I see it.

01:18:17.840 --> 01:18:21.982
I've seen the videos, people blaming the Lord for it.

01:18:21.982 --> 01:18:22.676
That's foolishness.

01:18:22.676 --> 01:18:25.770
I'm not going to go there and say that.

01:18:25.770 --> 01:18:30.030
You've got to know we live in a fallen world.

01:18:30.030 --> 01:18:31.030
Bad things happen.

01:18:31.030 --> 01:18:32.160
Things happen.

01:18:42.000 --> 01:18:43.408
We plead the blood, though, and we keep standing when all else there is to do is stand.

01:18:43.408 --> 01:18:44.464
Stand therefore.

01:18:44.464 --> 01:18:47.440
That's what you have to do.

01:18:47.440 --> 01:18:50.920
Because I'm telling you, you see storms.

01:18:50.920 --> 01:18:51.920
Storms happen.

01:18:51.920 --> 01:18:57.800
I don't know who that was for, but I'm trying to help somebody.

01:19:01.819 --> 01:19:02.239
And it's just in my heart to say that, to lift your head up in these dark hours.

01:19:02.239 --> 01:19:05.080
It's not time to get down.

01:19:05.080 --> 01:19:13.200
It's time to be happy and be excited because our redeemer is coming and the greatest harvest of souls, the greatest outpouring.

01:19:13.200 --> 01:19:14.910
I'm telling you, I've seen a plague.

01:19:14.910 --> 01:19:20.160
I've seen a plague that kills hundreds of millions of people.

01:19:20.560 --> 01:19:28.613
And there'll be good ones to go, and there'll be bad ones to go if this plague happens the way I saw it.

01:19:30.329 --> 01:19:30.587
And it's just the facts.

01:19:30.587 --> 01:19:32.180
It's what I've seen.

01:19:32.180 --> 01:19:36.948
And people go, "Why can't you stop some of this, Brandon?

01:19:36.948 --> 01:19:39.280
Some of these things are going to happen.

01:19:39.280 --> 01:19:41.552
" He said, "There'll be plagues.

01:19:41.552 --> 01:19:43.536
There'll be wars.

01:19:43.536 --> 01:19:46.137
There'll be rumors of wars.

01:19:47.679 --> 01:19:48.253
There's going to be famines.

01:19:48.253 --> 01:19:51.600
This is the beginning of sorrows.

01:19:51.600 --> 01:19:55.600
" Are we in the end times or not?

01:19:55.600 --> 01:19:59.337
This is the beginning of sorrows.

01:20:08.194 --> 01:20:08.629
We're going to see some things.

01:20:14.940 --> 01:20:15.860
But I believe as for me and my house, we are going to stay on the right side of him, be protected.

01:20:24.719 --> 01:20:24.950
And if not, to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

01:20:26.800 --> 01:20:27.573
You know, I'm not going to get in there.

01:20:27.573 --> 01:20:28.862
It's just stinking thinking.

01:20:28.862 --> 01:20:33.560
So, Father, we just lift up this prayer time before you, Father.

01:20:33.560 --> 01:20:35.840
We just come before you boldly tonight, Father.

01:20:35.840 --> 01:20:37.182
We thank you, Lord.

01:20:37.182 --> 01:20:40.560
We lift up every single person who's needing something, Father.

01:20:42.293 --> 01:20:46.320
And we just thank you, Lord, they're healed and whole and well in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:20:46.320 --> 01:20:48.240
God is a good God.

01:20:48.240 --> 01:20:55.320
God is a good God and the devil's a bad devil.

01:20:56.376 --> 01:21:05.217
And Father, I thank you, Lord, for your goodness and your mercy is going to follow us all the days of our life, and we dwell in the house of the Lord forever.

01:21:05.217 --> 01:21:10.571
You prepare a table before me in the presence of all my enemies.

01:21:10.571 --> 01:21:12.400
Thank you, Lord.

01:21:12.400 --> 01:21:14.320
My cup runneth over today.

01:21:14.320 --> 01:21:16.604
We're going from glory to glory.

01:21:16.604 --> 01:21:30.080
He's changing us, changing us, changing us from likeness and image to perfecting me, the love of God shown to the world.

01:21:37.493 --> 01:21:38.227
For he's changing, he's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:21:38.227 --> 01:21:43.199
His likeness and image to perfecting me, the love of God shown to the world.

01:21:54.070 --> 01:21:54.355
For he's changing, he's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:21:54.355 --> 01:21:58.100
His likeness and image to perfecting me, the love of God shown to the world.

01:21:58.100 --> 01:22:17.093
From glory to glory, he's changing me, changing me, changing me, his likeness and image to perfecting me, the love of God shown to the world, for he's changing, he's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:22:17.093 --> 01:22:24.000
Father, we just thank you, Lord, that you're changing us today.

01:22:24.000 --> 01:22:29.320
You're making us more like you every single day, from glory to glory.

01:22:29.320 --> 01:22:36.050
He's changing me, changing me, changing me, his likeness and image to perfecting me.

01:22:36.050 --> 01:22:39.786
The love of God shown to the world.

01:22:53.049 --> 01:22:54.359
For he's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:23:04.605 --> 01:23:05.874
Thank you, Lord.

01:23:21.190 --> 01:23:21.460
Lord, we worship you today.

01:23:21.460 --> 01:23:25.552
For you are good and your mercy endures forever.

01:23:45.684 --> 01:23:46.453
For the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever.

01:23:46.453 --> 01:23:53.640
Great is your faithfulness to us, Father, for all that you've done and all that you had to do.

01:23:53.640 --> 01:24:00.559
From glory to glory, you're changing us in his likeness and image, to perfect in me the love of God shown to the world.

01:24:00.559 --> 01:24:01.840
For he's changing.

01:24:01.840 --> 01:24:03.863
Do you believe it today?

01:24:03.863 --> 01:24:06.898
He's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:24:06.898 --> 01:24:09.320
Oh Father, we give you praise and glory.

01:24:09.320 --> 01:24:12.301
Oh Lord, we thank you for your grace.

01:24:15.680 --> 01:24:15.893
I believe in miracles.

01:24:17.920 --> 01:24:18.160
I see a soul set free.

01:24:18.160 --> 01:24:20.410
Miraculous the change in one redeemed through Calvary.

01:24:20.410 --> 01:24:24.756
I've seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

01:24:26.533 --> 01:24:28.380
I believe in miracles for I believe in God.

01:24:28.380 --> 01:24:29.679
I believe in miracles.

01:24:29.679 --> 01:24:32.400
I've seen a soul set free.

01:24:32.400 --> 01:24:35.733
Miraculous the change in one redeemed through Calvary.

01:24:35.733 --> 01:24:38.960
I've seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

01:24:38.960 --> 01:24:42.080
I believe in miracles for I believe in God.

01:24:42.080 --> 01:24:49.726
The glorious church will arise for the greatest outpouring of the spirit of the Lord beyond all comprehension is about to take place.

01:24:49.726 --> 01:24:51.710
The greatest manifestations and demonstrations.

01:25:07.662 --> 01:25:07.991
He saves the best for last.

01:25:07.991 --> 01:25:14.337
Glory to God for an outpouring of the spirit of the Lord is standing at your door.

01:25:14.337 --> 01:25:16.080
They come for I believe in miracles.

01:25:16.080 --> 01:25:20.267
I've seen a soul set free.

